cc:Work.dc:title: Tux The penguin in sonic style
cc:Work.dc:description: This is an idea i have from long ago, there are lots of copys of mario games out there with tux, but not any sonic-like game with tux or with any of the many animal mascots we have in the free software world :P Some time after i made him i started thinking he would be better not as a fast guy but as a strong one cause that body is far from the body of a penguin xD but a big fat-and-strong dude could look better :P othr of the mascots can be the fast guy I swear sooner or later im gonna do a game like that xD well this is if i remember well my third work on inkscape so it doesnt look as good as i would like
